- Graphics class:
    Draw textures
    Draw primitives (rectangles, circles, etc.)

- Input handling
    Key presses
    Mouse inputs

- Network class:
    Peer-to-peer connections

- Vector class (vec2)
    Matrix by vector
    Number by vector
    Vector by vector

- Character controller class
    Jump
    Walk
    Move around

- Representation of geometry (How will maps be stored?):
    Be able to collide with maps with little computation (geometry traversal)
    Be able to render maps easily

- Camera class (for viewing the world):
    Follow the player with camera
